        "cooked": "<p>I would both expand and simplify this request and say ‚Äúsupport markdown‚Äù. I know Signal does italics, bold, monospace now, but it‚Äôs all through the context menu. If it just supported markdown, we could do all of that as well as bullet points and such just by typing.</p>",
